    {
      "type": "text", "id": "rev-content", "x": 70, "y": 355, "width": 660, "height": 450,
      "text": "PER WEBINAR:\n175 registrants × $10 CPR = $1,750 ad spend\n→ 40% show rate = 70 attendees\n→ 10% conversion = 7 sales\n→ 7 × $997 = $6,979 revenue\n→ + 1-2 agency upsells × $5K/mo\n\nMONTHLY PROJECTION:\nMonth 1: $35-41K (building)\nMonth 2: $50K+ (agency recurring)\nMonth 3: $70-90K (compounding)\nMonth 6: $160-220K (live + evergreen)\n\nROAS: 7.1x ($7K in → $50K+ out)\n\nAGENCY COMPOUND EFFECT:\n4 new clients/mo × $5K = $20K new\n+ recurring from prior months\nMonth 3: 12 clients × $5K = $60K/mo",
      "fontSize": 16, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null, "originalText": "PER WEBINAR:\n175 registrants × $10 CPR = $1,750 ad spend\n→ 40% show rate = 70 attendees\n→ 10% conversion = 7 sales\n→ 7 × $997 = $6,979 revenue\n→ + 1-2 agency upsells × $5K/mo\n\nMONTHLY PROJECTION:\nMonth 1: $35-41K (building)\nMonth 2: $50K+ (agency recurring)\nMonth 3: $70-90K (compounding)\nMonth 6: $160-220K (live + evergreen)\n\nROAS: 7.1x ($7K in → $50K+ out)\n\nAGENCY COMPOUND EFFECT:\n4 new clients/mo × $5K = $20K new\n+ recurring from prior months\nMonth 3: 12 clients × $5K = $60K/mo",
      "autoResize": true, "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 2, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100,
