    {
      "type": "text", "id": "traffic-content", "x": 70, "y": 925, "width": 660, "height": 410,
      "text": "PAID (Primary — $100/day):\n• Facebook/Instagram Ads\n• 2 ad sets × 5 creatives (dynamic)\n• Broad targeting + Interest-based\n• Retargeting: site visitors + engaged\n• Lookalikes: leads + buyers\n• Target: $10 CPR\n\nORGANIC:\n• Instagram reels/stories (3-5/week)\n• Skool community posts (weekly)\n• YouTube Shorts (webinar teasers)\n• Email blast (Tuesdays)\n• SMS blast (Tue + Thu AM)\n\nTARGETING:\n• Clinic/practice owners, dentists,\n  chiropractors, med spa owners\n• US, age 28-55\n• Top markets: FL, TX, CA, NY",
      "fontSize": 16, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null, "originalText": "PAID (Primary — $100/day):\n• Facebook/Instagram Ads\n• 2 ad sets × 5 creatives (dynamic)\n• Broad targeting + Interest-based\n• Retargeting: site visitors + engaged\n• Lookalikes: leads + buyers\n• Target: $10 CPR\n\nORGANIC:\n• Instagram reels/stories (3-5/week)\n• Skool community posts (weekly)\n• YouTube Shorts (webinar teasers)\n• Email blast (Tuesdays)\n• SMS blast (Tue + Thu AM)\n\nTARGETING:\n• Clinic/practice owners, dentists,\n  chiropractors, med spa owners\n• US, age 28-55\n• Top markets: FL, TX, CA, NY",
      "autoResize": true, "lineHeight": 1.25,
