    {
      "type": "text", "id": "lp-content", "x": 870, "y": 355, "width": 710, "height": 290,
      "text": "healthproceo.com/webinar\nAll pages use auto-rolling Thursday dates\n\n V1: /webinar — Light theme (Control)\n V2: /webinar/v2 — Dark navy, form above fold\n V3: /webinar/v3 — Gold + black premium\n V4: /webinar/v4 — Cream + sky (brand colors)\n\nCONVERSION ELEMENTS:\n• Countdown timer to next Thursday\n• Seat counter (session-persisted)\n• PostHog + Meta + Hyros tracking\n• Practice type in registration form\n• 5 calendar options post-registration\n\nTarget: 35%+ registration rate",
      "fontSize": 16, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null, "originalText": "healthproceo.com/webinar\nAll pages use auto-rolling Thursday dates\n\n V1: /webinar — Light theme (Control)\n V2: /webinar/v2 — Dark navy, form above fold\n V3: /webinar/v3 — Gold + black premium\n V4: /webinar/v4 — Cream + sky (brand colors)\n\nCONVERSION ELEMENTS:\n• Countdown timer to next Thursday\n• Seat counter (session-persisted)\n• PostHog + Meta + Hyros tracking\n• Practice type in registration form\n• 5 calendar options post-registration\n\nTarget: 35%+ registration rate",
