    {
      "type": "text", "id": "nurture-content", "x": 870, "y": 775, "width": 710, "height": 490,
      "text": "IMMEDIATELY (Registration):\n  SMS: Confirmation + date + calendar link\n  Email: What to expect + case study teaser\n  Calendar: Google, Apple, Outlook, Office365, Yahoo\n\nWEDNESDAY (Day Before):\n  10 AM — SMS: \"Quick reminder — tomorrow at 7 PM\"\n  10 AM — Email: Social proof + full details + join link\n\nTHURSDAY (Day Of — Triple Touch):\n  9:00 AM — SMS: \"Today's the day!\"\n  6:00 PM — SMS: \"60 minutes! Join link inside\"\n  6:30 PM — Email: Join link + checklist + last details\n  7:00 PM — SMS: \"We're LIVE! Join now: [link]\"\n  7:05 PM — SMS (no-shows only): \"You're missing it\"\n  7:15 PM — Email (no-shows only): \"Still time to join\"\n\nGHL WORKFLOW: \"Webinar Pre-Show Nurture\"\nTRIGGER: Tag 'webinar-registered'\nEXIT: Webinar starts or tag 'webinar-attended'",
      "fontSize": 16, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null, "originalText": "IMMEDIATELY (Registration):\n  SMS: Confirmation + date + calendar link\n  Email: What to expect + case study teaser\n  Calendar: Google, Apple, Outlook, Office365, Yahoo\n\nWEDNESDAY (Day Before):\n  10 AM — SMS: \"Quick reminder — tomorrow at 7 PM\"\n  10 AM — Email: Social proof + full details + join link\n\nTHURSDAY (Day Of — Triple Touch):\n  9:00 AM — SMS: \"Today's the day!\"\n  6:00 PM — SMS: \"60 minutes! Join link inside\"\n  6:30 PM — Email: Join link + checklist + last details\n  7:00 PM — SMS: \"We're LIVE! Join now: [link]\"\n  7:05 PM — SMS (no-shows only): \"You're missing it\"\n  7:15 PM — Email (no-shows only): \"Still time to join\"\n\nGHL WORKFLOW: \"Webinar Pre-Show Nurture\"\nTRIGGER: Tag 'webinar-registered'\nEXIT: Webinar starts or tag 'webinar-attended'",
