    {
      "type": "text", "id": "offer-content", "x": 1720, "y": 355, "width": 760, "height": 910,
      "text": "\"Predictable Patient Pipeline\" Program\nTotal Value: $18,154 → YOUR PRICE: $997\n(or 3 × $397)\n\nCORE DELIVERABLES:\n  Custom Campaign Audit ............. $1,500\n  12-Module FB Ads Masterclass ...... $997\n  AI Patient Acquisition Blueprint .. $1,500\n  10 Custom Ads (YOUR website, 48hr). $1,500\n  Skool Community — 1 year .......... $2,364\n  Weekly Webinar Access — 1 year .... $2,500\n  Personalized Scaling Roadmap ...... $500\n\nBONUS RESOURCES:\n  Ad Creative Swipe File (50+ ads) .. $497\n  Operations Autopilot Templates .... $997\n  SPY + 253 Method Playbooks ........ $297\n  4 AI Playbooks .................... $1,200\n\nLIVE ATTENDEE BONUS (Sun midnight):\n  1-on-1 Pipeline Audit Call ........ $500\n  Private Slack — 30 days ........... $2,000\n  Done-for-you first campaign ....... $1,500\n\nGUARANTEE:\n  30-day money-back guarantee\n\nCHECKOUT: Whop or Stripe\nROI PITCH: \"2 extra patients = paid for itself\"",
      "fontSize": 16, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null, "originalText": "\"Predictable Patient Pipeline\" Program\nTotal Value: $18,154 → YOUR PRICE: $997\n(or 3 × $397)\n\nCORE DELIVERABLES:\n  Custom Campaign Audit ............. $1,500\n  12-Module FB Ads Masterclass ...... $997\n  AI Patient Acquisition Blueprint .. $1,500\n  10 Custom Ads (YOUR website, 48hr). $1,500\n  Skool Community — 1 year .......... $2,364\n  Weekly Webinar Access — 1 year .... $2,500\n  Personalized Scaling Roadmap ...... $500\n\nBONUS RESOURCES:\n  Ad Creative Swipe File (50+ ads) .. $497\n  Operations Autopilot Templates .... $997\n  SPY + 253 Method Playbooks ........ $297\n  4 AI Playbooks .................... $1,200\n\nLIVE ATTENDEE BONUS (Sun midnight):\n  1-on-1 Pipeline Audit Call ........ $500\n  Private Slack — 30 days ........... $2,000\n  Done-for-you first campaign ....... $1,500\n\nGUARANTEE:\n  30-day money-back guarantee\n\nCHECKOUT: Whop or Stripe\nROI PITCH: \"2 extra patients = paid for itself\"",
