    {
      "type": "text", "id": "w2-text", "x": 470, "y": 1470, "width": 330, "height": 220,
      "text": "PART 1: THE HOOK — 10 min\n\nWhy 90% of clinic marketing fails:\n1. Wrong targeting\n2. Slow follow-up (mins not days)\n3. No system (random tactics)\n\n\"You're losing $10K-50K/month in\npatients you already generate but\ndon't convert\"",
      "fontSize": 14, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top",
