      "text": "PART 2: CREDIBILITY — 15 min\n\n3 Case Studies (real numbers):\n\n• Houston Med Spa:\n  $20K → $131K/mo (21.7x ROAS)\n\n• All About Beautiful Smiles:\n  $142K → $202K/mo (19.4x ROAS)\n\n• Vitality & Aesthetics:\n  $5K → $38K/mo (12.9x ROAS)\n\n\"None worked more hours.\nThey installed a SYSTEM.\"",
      "fontSize": 14, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null, "originalText": "PART 2: CREDIBILITY — 15 min\n\n3 Case Studies (real numbers):\n\n• Houston Med Spa:\n  $20K → $131K/mo (21.7x ROAS)\n\n• All About Beautiful Smiles:\n  $142K → $202K/mo (19.4x ROAS)\n\n• Vitality & Aesthetics:\n  $5K → $38K/mo (12.9x ROAS)\n\n\"None worked more hours.\nThey installed a SYSTEM.\"",
