    {
      "type": "text", "id": "w4-text", "x": 1230, "y": 1470, "width": 380, "height": 220,
      "text": "PART 3: THE FRAMEWORK — 25 min\n\n3 AI Systems:\n\n1. AI Patient Acquisition\n   Chatbots + voice agents\n   < 60 second response time\n\n2. Content & Ad Engine\n   253 Method + SPY Method\n   AI creative tools demo\n\n3. Operations Autopilot\n   No-show reduction (50% cut)\n   Reactivation + review automation",
