    {
      "type": "text", "id": "webinar-flow-label", "x": 220, "y": 1730, "width": 2260, "height": 250,
      "text": "WEBINAR FLOW: Pre-Show (5m) ──→ Hook (10m) ──→ Credibility (15m) ──→ Framework (25m) ──→ Stack + Q&A (35m)\n\nKEY RULES:\n• Give the WHAT and WHY completely. Give enough HOW to prove expertise — but make it clear full implementation is complex.\n• Show real dashboards/screenshots for case studies — not slides with numbers.\n• The Pipeline Audit Call bonus is the TROJAN HORSE — it's where agency upsells happen.\n• \"Whether you join or not, go implement the SPY Method tonight\" — give them a win regardless.\n\nPLATFORM: Zoom Webinar or StreamYard  |  RECORDING: Yes — becomes replay for no-shows",
      "fontSize": 16, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null, "originalText": "WEBINAR FLOW: Pre-Show (5m) ──→ Hook (10m) ──→ Credibility (15m) ──→ Framework (25m) ──→ Stack + Q&A (35m)\n\nKEY RULES:\n• Give the WHAT and WHY completely. Give enough HOW to prove expertise — but make it clear full implementation is complex.\n• Show real dashboards/screenshots for case studies — not slides with numbers.\n• The Pipeline Audit Call bonus is the TROJAN HORSE — it's where agency upsells happen.\n• \"Whether you join or not, go implement the SPY Method tonight\" — give them a win regardless.\n\nPLATFORM: Zoom Webinar or StreamYard  |  RECORDING: Yes — becomes replay for no-shows",
      "autoResize": true, "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 2, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100,
