      "text": "Tag: 'webinar-attended'\n\nTHURSDAY 8:30 PM:\n  SMS + Email: Blueprint delivery + offer link + replay\n\nFRIDAY 10 AM:\n  SMS + Email: Case study deep dive\n  \"12 appointments in WEEK ONE\"\n\nSATURDAY 10 AM:\n  SMS + Email: Social proof + objection handling\n  \"I was skeptical, but...\"\n\nSUNDAY 10 AM:\n  SMS + Email: Deadline reminder — \"Last day\"\n\nSUNDAY 6 PM:\n  SMS: \"6 hours left\"\n\nSUNDAY 9 PM:\n  Email: \"3 hours\" — final email\n\nSUNDAY 11 PM:\n  SMS: \"1 hour left\" — last touch\n\nGHL WORKFLOW: \"Webinar Attendee Follow-Up\"\nEXIT: Tag 'pipeline-purchased' or cart closes",
