    {
      "type": "text", "id": "notpurchased-content", "x": 870, "y": 3205, "width": 660, "height": 310,
      "text": "Tag: 'webinar-no-buy'\n\nPATH 1: 7-Day Email Nurture\n  Existing sequence (Days 0-7)\n  Case studies + AI tools + frameworks\n  CTA: Roadmap, Sales Page, Strategy Call\n\nPATH 2: Downsell to $197 Course\n  \"Not ready for the full program?\n  Start with the FB Ads Course\"\n\nPATH 3: Re-Enter Next Webinar\n  Tuesday email: \"Join us this Thursday\"\n  New angle/hook each week\n\nPATH 4: Community Invite (Skool)\n  Free community as soft entry point\n  Weekly exposure → eventual conversion\n\nNO LEAD LEFT BEHIND — every path\nleads back to the webinar funnel",
