    {
      "type": "text", "id": "agency-content", "x": 1670, "y": 3205, "width": 810, "height": 430,
      "text": "TRIGGER: Pipeline Audit Call (from $997 purchase)\n         + Skool community engagement signals\n\nWHAT THEY GET ($5K/month × 4 months):\n\nMONTH 1 — FOUNDATION\n  Full marketing audit + competitive analysis\n  AI appointment setter setup (voice + chat)\n  First 3 ad campaigns launched\n  GHL automation buildout\n  Weekly strategy call\n\nMONTH 2 — OPTIMIZATION\n  Scale winners, kill losers\n  Patient reactivation campaigns\n  Review automation active\n  A/B testing creative\n\nMONTH 3 — SCALE\n  New audience segments + retargeting\n  Messenger/chatbot campaigns\n  Optimize for ROAS\n\nMONTH 4 — HANDOFF OR RETAIN\n  Full documentation + team training\n  Option: continue at $5K/mo ongoing\n  Many stay 6-12 months ($60-72K LTV)\n\nCONVERSION: 15-20% of $997 buyers = 1-2/webinar",
      "fontSize": 16, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null, "originalText": "TRIGGER: Pipeline Audit Call (from $997 purchase)\n         + Skool community engagement signals\n\nWHAT THEY GET ($5K/month × 4 months):\n\nMONTH 1 — FOUNDATION\n  Full marketing audit + competitive analysis\n  AI appointment setter setup (voice + chat)\n  First 3 ad campaigns launched\n  GHL automation buildout\n  Weekly strategy call\n\nMONTH 2 — OPTIMIZATION\n  Scale winners, kill losers\n  Patient reactivation campaigns\n  Review automation active\n  A/B testing creative\n\nMONTH 3 — SCALE\n  New audience segments + retargeting\n  Messenger/chatbot campaigns\n  Optimize for ROAS\n\nMONTH 4 — HANDOFF OR RETAIN\n  Full documentation + team training\n  Option: continue at $5K/mo ongoing\n  Many stay 6-12 months ($60-72K LTV)\n\nCONVERSION: 15-20% of $997 buyers = 1-2/webinar",
      "autoResize": true, "lineHeight": 1.25,
