    {
      "type": "text", "id": "kpi-content", "x": 70, "y": 3785, "width": 1160, "height": 310,
      "text": "WEEKLY TARGETS:\n  Registration rate (ad click → register): 35%+\n  Show-up rate (registered → attended): 45%+\n  Offer conversion (attendees → buyers): 10-15%\n  Replay conversion (no-shows → buyers): 5%+\n  Cost per registrant: < $12\n  Revenue per registrant: $50+\n  Weekly revenue: $12,500+\n  Monthly ROAS: 7x+\n\nOPTIMIZATION PRIORITY (in order):\n  1. Show-up rate — biggest revenue lever\n  2. Offer conversion — webinar content + pitch\n  3. Registration rate — ads + landing page\n  4. Replay conversion — no-show sequence\n  5. Cost per registrant — ad efficiency",
